iv><div class="t m0 x22 h4 y193 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">因此，<span class="_ _3"></span>今天就一起来探讨：<span class="_ _3"></span>人活在这个世界上，<span class="_ _3"></span>到底需</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y194 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">要希求什么样的真理？这种真理，<span class="_ _4"></span>从什么样的哲学思想中能</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y195 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">挖掘出来？我想，这也是很多老师和同学都愿意关注的。 </div><div class="t m0 x25 hc y196 ffc fs3 fc0 sc1 ls18 ws0">一、我们要怎样观察真理 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
